seller.description:
In the today's media-mad world, voice over is everywhere. But it takes much more than just a great voice to be a great communicator. I'm repeatedly told that people are impacted by my voice over and that what I say sticks with them!

My name is Chuck Brown. I've been a full-time professional VO for over 2 decades. My voice is naturally deep, authoritative, and easily understood. 

I've served as a key voice for major national and international brands. 

I'm available to lend my voice to your product or service as well. Thanks for your interest!
